title: Stable Diffusion Tip: How to get the result you want?
text:
If you want to produce good images with Stable Diffusion, produce at least 50 outputs. Even if you are using Finetune.

Even designers struggle to draw what you want its first time. So don't expect an AI to produce result you want on its first output.
